headline: Intuit Launches New Career Pipeline Program to Empower the Next Generation of Accountants in the AI Era
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., January 28, 2026--Intuit (NASDAQ: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, announced today its new Career Pipeline Program, committing to upskilling one million students in the accounting industry over the next five years.
